headline: Logility Supply Chain Solutions (LGTY) Surges 24.7%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Logility Supply Chain Solutions (LGTY) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
